column5: On our trip to Lake of the Woods we typically proceed on highway 371 to Cass Lake, and then take Hiway 2 east to Scenic Hiway 10 north which turns in to 39 to arrive at Blackduck. For several years there has been been detours and would appreciate a status regarding this route.
This should give you the info you need...http://hb.511mn.org/#roadReports/lay...ts,roadReportsFrank
